Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited Key Developments

Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited Announces Unaudited Consolidated and Company Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 15 17
Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited announced unaudited consolidated and company earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, on consolidated basis, the company reported profit attributable to the owners of the company of THB 144,490,000 or THB 0.42 per basic share compared to THB 135,388,000 THB 0.39 per basic share a year ago. Total revenue was THB 942,335,000 compared to THB 837,595,000 a year ago. Profit before income tax expense was THB 181,887,000 compared to THB 170,468,000 a year ago. Net cash from operating activities was THB 44,373,000 compared to THB 173,040,000 a year ago. Acquisition of property, plant and equipment was THB 10,887,000 compared to THB 1,102,125,000 a year ago.

For the quarter, on company basis, the company reported profit attributable to the owners of the company of THB 82,235,000 or THB 0.24 per basic share compared to THB 66,956,000 THB 0.19 per basic share a year ago. Total revenue was THB 579,206,000 compared to THB 514,165,000 a year ago. Profit before income tax expense was THB 103,266,000 compared to THB 84,147,000 a year ago. Net cash from operating activities was THB 94,752,000 compared to THB 32,855,000 a year ago. Acquisition of property, plant and equipment was THB 7,152,000 compared to THB 1,099,246,000 a year ago.


Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited Reappoints KPMG Phoomchai Audit Co. Ltd. as Auditor
Mar 29 17
Siam Pan Group Public Co. Ltd. at its AGM held on March 30, 2017, approved the appointment of Appoint KPMG Phoomchai Audit Ltd. By Ms. Napaporn Sathitthammaporn CPA Registration No. 7494 or Ms. Sureerat Thongarunsang CPA Registration No. 4409 or Ms. Pornthip Rimdusit CPA Registration No. 5565 to be the company's Auditor.


Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited, Annual General Meeting, Mar 29, 2017
Feb 10 17
Siam Pan Group Public Company Limited, Annual General Meeting, Mar 29, 2017, at 03:30 Coordinated Universal Time. Location: Rachadramnern Room of the Royal Princess Hotel 269 Larnluang Road, Pomprab Bangkok Thailand Agenda: To certify the minutes of 1/2016 the ordinary general meeting of shareholders; to acknowledge the company's operating results and the board of directors' report for the year 2016; to approve the audited statement of financial position and Statement of comprehensive income for the year ended December 31, 2016; to consider and approve the appropriation of net profit for legal reserves and dividend payments; to consider and appoint an auditor and fix the auditing fee for the year 2017; to consider the election of directors in place of those vacating the office by rotation; to consider and fix the directors' remuneration for the year 2017; and to consider other issues (if any).


