Products








Pineapple RetailTropical Fruit RetailPineapple BulkAnimal Feed 





  PRODUCTS FOR EVERY MARKET AND THE WORLD OVER Siam Food processes fruit products to meet the specific needs of any private label customer. The company is also working to develop innovative products to meet the unique requirements of a changing market place.Approximately 99% of Siam Food's products are exported to many major markets, such as the U.S.A., the United Kingdom, Japan, Scandinavia, Germany, the Netherlands, France, Italy and Spain. NOT JUST PINEAPPLESIn addition to all cuts of canned pineapple slices (choice, standard), chunks, tidbits, and crushed, Siam Food is also manufacturing pineapple juice concentrate, tropical fruit cocktail and others with ambition to respond consumption demands in selected markets. 
 

















 

















